mi energy,\notherwise the electron transport is blocked due to the absence of edge states.\nRemarkably, the number of oscillating peaks exactly matches to the number of\nsawtooth along an edge of PQD, since the discrete energy levels of the\nzigzag-like edge provide the transporting channels for electrons. The results\nhere may be extended to the group-VA 2D materials for observing the electronic\nproperty of nanostructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Dec 2019 13:38:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-13"}
