ying\nbroad features, LSQ13ddu appears deficient in He compared to standard SNe Ib.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Dec 2019 14:33:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Dec 2019 12:11:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-22"}
