ssential in soft tissue mechanobiology. For the first time ever, we measure\nand analyze 3D strain fields induced by these chemoelastic effects thanks to\nthe unique combination of OCT imaging and digital volume correlation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Dec 2019 15:53:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-19"}
